Package: shoredate
Title: Shoreline date sites on the Norwegian Skagerrak coast
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Isak", "Roalkvam", , "isakroa@protonmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6974-1374"))
Description: Provides tools for dating Stone Age sites located on the Norwegian Skagerrak coast based on their present day elevation and reconstructions of past sea-level change.
